            <a href="https://twitter.com/sra_eng"><i class="fab fa-twitter-square fa-3x"></i></a>
            <p></p>
            <p>Agendas and supporting documentation for SRA meetings are made available to the public the Wednesday before each meeting on the MSU website:</p>
